This paper deals with wireless communication networks and their optimization for energy efficiency and spectral efficiency. It also discusses non-orthogonal multiple access (NOMA) and time-division multiple access (TDMA) schemes. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
